content: Great tool for teaching, practice and learning rhythms that you otherwise can't find lessons for.
I am so disappointed because this app doesn't have any counts for the Beats. No numbers whatsoever to understand where all those syncopations fall on the measures.

Great app! An opportunity for improvement regarding tempo adjustment: Decreasing speed degrades audio quality MUCH more than increasing speed. Many rhythms are recorded at such fast tempos that the slower speeds don't sound good. I'd love to see updates that replace recordings with new ones that are recorded as slow as you are able to play while preserving the natural feel. It isn't easy to play so slow, but if you can, the sound quality will be amazing! Thank you for your work on this app!
Really fantastic. Is it possible to add some Son in future updates?
It's a nice app, I wish I could listen to it while doing something else in the phone. I should play along
replyContent: Hello, thanks for your review, please contact us to specify what you mean. "Background audio ?". Best

content: This app allows you to build an experience unique for you. The team is also willing to go out of their way to help! Would recommend!
GREAT app. *** What to IMPROVE ??? > ADD OPTION of DECREASE / INCREASE VOLUME per INSTRUMENT, instead of ONLY OVERALL VOLUME.
replyContent: Thanks a lot for your review. This is a great idea and some users asked us for that feature. We might one day but we chose not to because this gives the user the precise idea how the instrument should fit together.
